text:
Us din itna discuss kar liya still dont know pehli baar vibe kab kiye the. The first time we had that average wala discussion, mera outlook on lot of things changed drastically, it has been kinda peaceful. Literally har topic pe sabse intense aur in-depth discussions and analysis kiye hai apan ne lol. It was legit fun listening to your opinions on anything random xD. Vo ek *specific* movie dekhne gaye the aur judge hone se darr rahe the yaad hai? With time gossips ka nasha bhi chadha aur fir gossip ki trading bhi shuru hui thi lol.
Everytime it was pessimistic bhatia vs optimistic gosai. Placement ki bt ke time mera almost pura semester tu hi nikala hai and I didn't even have to ask for that. Tu kaafi sochta hai bhai thoda kam soch liya kar.
"Aage kuch bhi karega toh bata ke kariyo gosai" ye yaad rakhna tu bhi lmao.
Aur haan, professional friends toh nahi hi hai apan obviously. Ek trip saath me karni hai jaldi but uske pehle apna koi common group figure out kar lo xD
author: Gosai  Akash

text: Sirrrr, first year me tere pe meme banaya tha "Apun bhagwan hai" and the literal sense it holds now. Tera confidence kaafi inspiring hai bhai. Singapore jake bhulna nahi lol. Abhi aapse kaafi guidance leni bachi hai xD
author: Gosai  Akash

text: Probably the only person in a group of 5 who would avoid work more than me xD. First year winters me mile the apan tab tu bada chaapu lagta tha. Khair. Tumhara OS wala fuckup yaad rahega. Waise tumse har topic pe discussions interesting rahe hai. Football dekhna bhi shuru karna hai humne saath me. Touch me rahiyo hamesha.
author: Gosai  Akash

text: Bhandi wali debate kaafi badhiya thi bhai. "Mumbai aa raha hai na tu?" xD
author: Gosai  Akash

text: The only unblocked mutual xD Aakhri dino me kaafi maze aa gaye. Tumhari philosophical bakchodi kaafi enjoy ki hai. Would really love to learn more about qualia lmao. Also, I dont think paisa waisa is coming out anytime soon is it? Anyways mumbai me milenge ab bhai lol
author: Gosai  Akash

text:
Sharma boii meme culture pe top kiya karte the apan first year me. Underground rap saath me explore kiye the, uspe puri vibe set thi. Antaragni me bhi wahi carry karke RaGa logo ke saath photo le liye. 5 Suteri ftw. 
"Daaaal khaani hai yaar" xD Apne se zyada edgy koi nahi tha us period me bhai. Manali trip ki gutbaazi retrospect me kaafi fun lagti hai. Mere crush wale loche me teri punchlines pe kaafi hase the vo yaad rahega lmao. Delhi police FIR wale prank ko yaad karke abhi bhi chills aa jate hai bhai. 
Abhi IIMA jaake naam toh roshan kar hi diye ho humara, abhi aage aur chaapna hai. Ek aur goa trip rehti hai apni abhi saath me, inshallah woh be jald kar lenge <3
author: Gosai  Akash

text: "Mai tera best friend hu pata hai na tereko?" First year wala 7 din ka cold war yaad hai na? Bina kisi reason ke tha vo bhi. Campus pe har cheez me tumhe mai guide kiya hu but chalo kya hi flex karein. RED CSS me tumhare aRtIsTic skills dikh gaye the lmao. Zyada taarifein nahi karunga kyuki vo toh bhandi me kar hi diya hu lol. Teri hustle karne wali aadat kaafi badhiya hai. Meri intern ki bt me pure time saath tha tu, aur intern lagne pe bhi sabse zyada khush tu hi hua tha. Tumhare nakhro ki wajah se Divine wali shirt miss kar gaye uske liye hamesha galiyaenge. Mumbai darshan karna hai abhi saath me lol. Aur haan, block temporary hai xD.
author: Gosai  Akash

text:
"Apan dono ek dono ki mirror image hai, apan ko issues bhi same hi honge." Tumne apni nayi personality embrace kari uske baad se apni synergy kaafi badhi hai. First impression me tumhari smile badi creepy lagi thi. Tiktok cringe watch sessions miss karunga lmao keep em sending in my DMs. Nobody should know about mujhse shaadi karogi okay? Movie nights major missing. Antaragni me titanic scene recreate kiya tha apan ne which was pretty sweet.
Aur haan, betrayal video ki script tumne improve nahi kharab ki thi. Also, you really need to find a better aesthetic consultant.
author: Gosai  Akash

text: ART105 choose karte hi vibe kar gaye the apan. First time awaz suni thi toh kaafi disappoint hua tha, plus tu weeb bhi tha smh. Obviously you know now that I'm a better gamer than you. Cookie ke upar hui ladai (spark?) hamesha yaad rahegi lmao, Humse 5 saal bade ho iska kaafi advantage raha mujhe, kaafi kuch sikh gaya tumse lol. Mera free wala moral support raha hai tu lmao. Will remember the WWUD protocol. Vo rooftop wali video ka zikr na karna kabhi xD. Blind date wali hosting one of the best memories hogi lmao, Abhi aage IAS YAS bano aur naam roshan karo humara, and ofc 13/7 wala bhai hu mai <3
author: Gosai  Akash

text: Or bhai? Har shaam ka canteen partner. It'll always be mystery to me ke pure semester saari cheezein ek saath karne ke bawjood tu hamesha A me aur mai B me kyu rehta tha lmao. Dekhte hi dekhte tu kaafi bakchodho gaya, from "bhai kuch ML nahi aati" to securing that bag from CMU. Chaapu aur chill wala perfect combination hai tu. Last month me gala bhi tar liya saath me. OS plagiarism wale din will always haunt me for life xD. Ab seedha US aayenge bhai saath me party karenge.
author: Gosai  Akash

text: "6 QUEEEENS" woh bluff wali night kaafi fun thi lmao. D-139 me kaafi mulakat hoti thi tujhse. Utkarsh ko roast karne me accha support rehta tha tera. HSS form apan ne saath bhara tha aur tumhe bt mili thi voh yaad rahega lol. Bangalore aana hua toh karenge hangout saath me xD
